---
description: Core project guidance for the AI Agent Kit repository
alwaysApply: true
---

- This repository is a distributable agent kit, not an application runtime.
- The source of truth is `.agent/`.
- Keep `README.md` and `.agent/ARCHITECTURE.md` aligned with actual shipped contents.
- If you change packaging or installation behavior, verify with `npm pack --dry-run`.
- Keep IDE-specific adapter files thin and aligned with `.agent/`.
- Prefer updating existing agents, skills, and workflows over creating duplicate systems.
